OL,3,CShort-term lets to require planning
OL,4,Cpermission under new proposals
OL,6,FMichael Gove has announced proposals
OL,7,Fto require planning permission for
OL,8,Fshort-term lets to prevent a
OL,9,F"hollowing out" of communities.
OL,11,FThe new law would require people
OL,12,Fletting out their property as a short-
OL,13,Fterm holiday home to seek permission
OL,14,Ffrom the local authority under a new
OL,15,F"use" category.
OL,17,FThe rules would not to apply to people
OL,18,Frenting out their main home for 90
OL,19,Fdays or less in a year.
