OL,3,CShort-term lets to require planning
OL,4,Cpermission under new proposals
OL,6,FA mandatory national register would be
OL,7,Fset up providing councils with
OL,8,Finformation on short-term lets in
OL,9,Ftheir area.
OL,11,FMr Gove unveiled the plans during a
OL,12,Fvisit to the Cornish village of St
OL,13,FAgnes, in a bid to tackle the issue of
OL,14,Fshort-term lets leaving fewer places
OL,15,Ffor local people to live.
OL,17,FHe met with members of the community
OL,18,Fto discuss housing issues in the
OL,19,FDuchy, where there are 13,000 second
OL,20,Fhomes according to a 2022 council
OL,21,Freport.
