OL,3,CShort-term lets to require planning
OL,4,Cpermission under new proposals
OL,6,FThe Housing Secretary said: "We know
OL,7,Fthat in the short term it can be
OL,8,Fhelpful for the tourist economy but we
OL,9,Falso know that needs to be an element
OL,10,Fof control so that local people can
OL,11,Falso rent those homes as well."
OL,13,FThe Housing Secretary says this should
OL,14,Fprevent landlords in the future
OL,15,Fchanging the type of rental from long-
OL,16,Fterm to short-term without the
OL,17,Fcouncil's approval first.
