OL,3,CShort-term lets to require planning
OL,4,Cpermission under new proposals
OL,6,F"I think it's appropriate that people,
OL,7,Fif they want to, can let out their
OL,8,Fhomes part of the time, but they do
OL,9,Fneed to register", Mr Gove said.
OL,11,F"And then secondly, it's also the case
OL,12,Fthat if that home is currently being
OL,13,Fused in the in the private rented
OL,14,Fsector with a family there, that you
OL,15,Fneed to you apply for planning
OL,16,Fpermission in order to get that home
OL,17,Fto become a short term rental in the
OL,18,Ffuture.
