OL,3,CShort-term lets to require planning
OL,4,Cpermission under new proposals
OL,6,FLinda Taylor, leader of Cornwall
OL,7,FCouncil, welcomed the proposals to
OL,8,Ftackle the "escalating" number of
OL,9,Fholiday lets in the county.
OL,11,FShe said: "Alongside the introduction
OL,12,Fof the 100% premium on second homes
OL,13,Ffrom April 2025, I'm pleased the
OL,14,FGovernment is providing the fiscal,
OL,15,Fplanning and regulatory powers to help
OL,16,Frebalance Cornwall's housing market
OL,17,Fand allow us to provide even more
OL,18,Fdecent and secure homes for local
OL,19,Fpeople and help all our communities to
OL,20,Fthrive."
