OL,4,Cpermission under new proposals
OL,6,FA Department for Levelling Up, Housing
OL,7,Fand Communities spokesman said: "The
OL,8,FGovernment also intends to introduce
OL,9,Fassociated permitted development
OL,10,Frights ` one allowing for a property
OL,11,Fto be changed from a short-term let to
OL,12,Fa standard residential dwelling, and a
OL,13,Fsecond that would allow a property to
OL,14,Fbe changed to a short-term let.
OL,16,F"Local authorities would be able to
OL,17,Fremove these permissions and require
OL,18,Ffull planning permission if they deem
OL,19,Fit necessary.
