OL,3,CShort-term lets to require planning
OL,4,Cpermission under new proposals
OL,6,F"Both of these measures are focused on
OL,7,Fshort-term lets, and therefore the
OL,8,Fplanning changes and the register will
OL,9,Fnot affect hotels, hostels or B&Bs."
OL,11,F"Further details of these measures
OL,12,Fwill be set out in the Government's
OL,13,Fresponse to the consultations,
OL,14,Fincluding the timeline for
OL,15,Fimplementation of the register, the
OL,16,Fuse class and the individual permitted
OL,17,Fdevelopment rights ` with the changes
OL,18,Fbeing introduced from this summer."
